data.description: Remodeled 2 story townhouse close to everything in O'Fallon Illinois. Great for an investor, currently leased. The main level has a living room/dining room combo with new vinyl flooring, half bath with vinyl floor, kitchen with a sit-down eating area. Updated appliances include stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, disposal, washer and dryer. Kitchen closet houses washer and dryer with all hookups. Upper level has master bedroom with carpet & walk-in closet. Second Bedroom also has carpet. There is an extra closet in the hallway & full bathroom with vinyl flooring. Outside there is a new deck off back door as well as covered off street parking included. HOA covers roof, outside maintenance, landscaping, lawn care and snow removal. Covenants attached in supplements,  Passed O'Fallon inspection. Currently Leased, the rent is $925.00 per month, One Year lease, Call Brokers for Showings.
